\subsection{Implementation Status and Roadmap}
\begin{itemize}
    \item \textbf{Phase 1 (Testnet Alpha):} Q4 2025. PoT Challenge Generation prototype, basic NuVM deployment, and initial zkML Proof verification on a small private network.
    \item \textbf{Phase 2 (Public Testnet Beta):} Q2 2026. Public validator onboarding, full NuVM and Wasm compatibility, token staking/slashing implementation.
